text: Nicolae Ionel Ciucă (; born 7 February 1967) is a Romanian politician and retired general. He is a member of the Romanian Land Forces. He was the Prime Minister of Romania from 25 November 2021 to 12 June 2023. ==References== Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian generals Category:Current national leaders Category:Prime Ministers of Romania
